title: Unemployment rate in Cambodia 2019
summary: Overall Unemployment rate has decreased over the Year.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2000 and 2001.
Maximum Unemployment rate, about 2.45 was reported at Year 2000
Minimum Unemployment rate about 1.15 was reached at Year 2008
